name: Elliott Rosengarten O.D. PSC
tag_list: optometrist, louisville, ky, eye-doctor, eye-exams, eye-care, eyeglasses, contact-lenses
overview:
Elliott Rosengarten O.D. PSC is a group of optometrists located in an eye care clinic which serves Louisville, Kentucky. They offer eye care and eye exams for people with vision problems and also provide prescriptions for contacts and eyeglasses.

The eye care services offered at this Louisville, KY clinic are:

  • Comprehensive eye exams
  • Dry eye treatments
  • Glaucoma testing
  • Cataracts diagnosis and treatment
  • LASIK consultations
  • prescriptions for eyeglasses
  • Contact lens fittings
  • Macular degeneration treatment
  • Pediatric eye exams from a certified pediatric optometrist

In addition this Louisville optometry clinic offers a wide selection of eyewear and people can find designer frames from Armani and more. They also offer a number of designer frame sunglasses from brand name manufacturers at affordable prices.

They carry a variety of contact lenses which include:

  • Bifocal and multifocal contacts
  • Gas permeable contact lenses
  • Toric contacts for astigmatism
  • Daily disposable contact lenses

Elliott Rosengarten O.D. PSC serves the Louisville, KY area and the nearby locations of: Brownsboro Road and the Watterson.
